West_Palm_Beach.Stacy Street, Florida:
Stacy Street is a street and surrounding census-designated place (CDP) in Palm Beach County, Florida, United States. The population was 958 at the 2000 census, which misspelled it Stacey Street.


== Geography ==
Stacy Street stretches west from Haverhill Road for 0.4 miles (0.64 km) to a T intersection, where North and South Stacy Streets, two dead-end streets, lead in both directions.
